3186922894921516318.Text: Frald the White told me that Honthjolf, a former Knight Errant of the Order of Ebonheart, has made a pact with the Daedra worshippers of Aharnabi, which is on the far southeastern shores of Azura's coast, near the Shrine of Azura. Honthjolf is a traitor to the Order and must be killed.

24006245331514017420.Text: Frald the White thanked me for killing Honthjolf, the traitor to our Order.

23577167122243321851.Text: Imperial Legion: Honthjolf is a Traitor
